## What NOT to do

- **Never edit** `graph/generated/generated.go` or `graph/model/models_gen.go` â€” run `make api-generate`
- **Never commit** `.env` â€” only `.env.example`
- **Never use `fmt.Sprintf` to build SQL** â€” use parameterized `$N` placeholders
- **Never hardcode brand colors** â€” use Mantine color refs or CSS vars
- **Never use Tailwind utility classes** â€” use Mantine style props or inline styles
- **Never add** `node_modules/` or `dist/` to git

